==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: heavyweight
<hw>heavyweight</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a wrestler who
weighs more than 214 pounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a boxer who weighs more than 195 pounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>a very large person.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> giant, hulk.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>a person of exceptional importance and
reputation.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> colossus, behemoth, giant, titan.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

